statements: SELECT * FROM TradeExecutionData WHERE trade_id = 1;
SELECT symbol, quantity, price FROM TradeExecutionData WHERE trade_date = '2022-10-15';
SELECT trade_id, symbol, quantity FROM TradeExecutionData WHERE price > 1000 ORDER BY trade_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM TradeExecutionData WHERE strategy_id = 5 ORDER BY trade_date ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT symbol FROM TradeExecutionData WHERE quantity >= 1000 ORDER BY symbol ASC, execution_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM TradeExecutionData WHERE trade_id = 100;
SELECT symbol, quantity, price FROM TradeExecutionData WHERE trade_date >= '2021-01-01' ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT trade_id, symbol, quantity, price FROM TradeExecutionData WHERE strategy_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT symbol, execution_time FROM TradeExecutionData WHERE trade_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM TradeExecutionData WHERE price >= 100 ORDER BY trade_date DESC, trade_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data
SELECT symbol, price FROM trade_execution_data WHERE quantity > 100
SELECT trade_id, symbol, timestamp FROM trade_execution_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT * FROM trading_strategies WHERE performance_score > 90
SELECT strategy_name, performance_score FROM trading_strategies ORDER BY performance_score DESC
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data WHERE symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT trade_id, symbol, quantity FROM trade_execution_data WHERE price > 100.00 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT symbol, quantity, price FROM trade_execution_data WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT symbol, SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM trade_execution_data GROUP BY symbol HAVING total_quantity > 500;
SELECT * FROM trading_strategies WHERE start_date < '2022-06-01' AND end_date > '2022-06-01' ORDER BY performance_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM trade_executions ORDER BY trade_date DESC, execution_price ASC
SELECT symbol, executed_quantity FROM trade_executions WHERE execution_price > 100 ORDER BY trade_date
SELECT execution_id, symbol, execution_price FROM trade_executions WHERE executed_quantity < 1000
SELECT * FROM strategy_executions WHERE execution_result = 'Success' ORDER BY execution_time DESC
SELECT strategy_name, strategy_description FROM trading_strategies
SELECT * FROM trade_executions ORDER BY trade_date DESC, execution_price ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT execution_id, symbol, executed_quantity FROM trade_executions WHERE trade_date >= '2022-01-01' AND trade_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT symbol, execution_price, machine_learning_model FROM trade_executions WHERE executed_quantity > 1000 ORDER BY execution_price DESC;
SELECT trade_date, symbol, execution_price, executed_quantity FROM trade_executions WHERE machine_learning_model LIKE '%random_forest%' LIMIT 5;

SELECT se.execution_time, ts.strategy_name, ts.strategy_performance FROM strategy_executions se LEFT JOIN trading_strategies ts ON se.strategy_id = ts.strategy_id ORDER BY se.execution_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM trades;
SELECT trade_id, symbol, price FROM trades WHERE quantity > 100;
SELECT trade_id, symbol, execution_timestamp FROM trades ORDER BY execution_timestamp DESC;
SELECT t.symbol, tp.profit_loss, tp.success FROM trades t JOIN trade_performance tp ON t.trade_id = tp.trade_id WHERE tp.profit_loss > 0;
SELECT ts.strategy_name, count(st.trade_id) AS total_trades FROM trade_strategies ts LEFT JOIN strategy_trades st ON ts.strategy_id = st.strategy_id GROUP BY ts.strategy_name HAVING total_trades > 5;
SELECT * FROM trades;
SELECT symbol, quantity, price FROM trades WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY price DESC;

SELECT t.symbol, ts.strategy_name, tp.profit_loss FROM trades t JOIN strategy_trades st ON t.trade_id = st.trade_id JOIN trade_strategies ts ON st.strategy_id = ts.strategy_id LEFT JOIN trade_performance tp ON tp.trade_id = t.trade_id WHERE tp.success = TRUE;

SELECT DISTINCT ts.strategy_name, COUNT(t.trade_id) AS total_trades FROM trade_strategies ts JOIN strategy_trades st ON ts.strategy_id = st.strategy_id JOIN trades t ON st.trade_id = t.trade_id GROUP BY ts.strategy_name HAVING total_trades > 5 ORDER BY total_trades DESC;
SELECT t.symbol, t.quantity, tp.profit_loss, tp.success FROM trades t LEFT JOIN trade_performance tp ON t.trade_id = tp.trade_id WHERE t.quantity * t.price > 1000 AND tp.success IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data ORDER BY trade_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT symbol, trade_price, executed_quantity FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_price > 100 ORDER BY trade_price ASC;
SELECT strategy_name, total_trades, total_profit FROM strategy_performance WHERE total_trades > 50 ORDER BY total_profit DESC;
SELECT * FROM trade_analysis WHERE success_rate >= 80 AND analysis_result LIKE '%positive%' ORDER BY analysis_timestamp ASC;
SELECT strategy_name, strategy_description FROM trade_strategy;
SELECT * FROM trade_execution_data ORDER BY trade_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT trade_id, trade_price, strategy_name FROM trade_execution_data WHERE trade_price > 100 ORDER BY trade_price ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT symbol, trade_timestamp, executed_quantity, strategy_name FROM trade_execution_data WHERE symbol = 'AAPL' ORDER BY trade_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT strategy_name, total_profit, average_return FROM strategy_performance WHERE total_profit > 10000 ORDER BY total_profit DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT analysis_id, trade_id, analysis_timestamp, trading_strategy, success_rate FROM trade_analysis WHERE success_rate > 80 ORDER BY analysis_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
